content: असमस्त {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Incomplete, imperfect, partial, not whole. {@--2@} (In <ab>gram.</ab>) Not joined in a compound, not compounded. {@--3@} Uncollected. {@--4@} Separate, detached, unconnected (<ab>opp.</ab> व्यस्त). --स्तं An uncompounded word (the sentence showing the dissolution of a compound).
